{"tid":1318991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［拋磚引玉］攪 大 沙 田 商 場 連 儂 牆","createTime":"2019-07-15T05:18:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-15T08:19:41.000Z","uid":213379,"like":290,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"409944dac65a8e2765fdebd69d36e74c9fa691e9","tid":1318991,"uid":213379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-15T05:18:14.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">1）向自由行宣傳革命精神</span></span></strong><br />\n由沙田站 新城市出口做起 <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">而地理位置上 所有連橋位置都可以係連儂牆</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">2）借力打力</span></span></strong><br />\n中共見聞連儂牆包圍住沙田所有商場<br />\n一定放風話沙田新城市及其商場 唔適合自由行去<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">變相制裁哂所有放警察入去既商場</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3）連結老中青</span></strong></span><br />\n今次沙田一仗 打通左老中青三代人關係<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">請沙田友叫屋企老人家 老豆 老母 <br />\n落去貼滿哂沙田新城市及周圍所有商場 <br />\n</span>咁當然夏天咁熱 去商場嘆住冷氣 <br />\nMon下連儂牆都可以 <br />\n令今次抗爭活動 唔係得後生仔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">歡迎各位補充及討論！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">同場放映：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n如果大家畀左3蚊支持蘋果日報 可以用同一個帳號 Click入下面條Link睇到！請廣傳<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.feature.appledaily.com/goodestchannel/video/5d039937f1756a00060be77a/%E5%9C%B0%E5%8E%9A%E5%A4%A9%E9%AB%98%20Lost%20in%20the%20Fumes%20(2017%20%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF)?fb_comment_id=2249537475142295_2257875277641848\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.feature.appledaily.com%2Fgoodestchannel%2Fvideo%2F5d039937f1756a00060be77a%2F%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%258E%259A%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E9%25AB%2598%2520Lost%2520in%2520the%2520Fumes%2520%282017%2520%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%29%3Ffb_comment_id%3D2249537475142295_2257875277641848&d=MD3su0BfWHBnm8Iidd6ZKezNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=11be4fd0\" data-ef-u